1. follow link to download mongo DB
   https://www.mongodb.com/download-center#community
   install it on your syatem.
2. create one folder on your system for database use.
3. Set path for mongo db   
   -Open cmd and go to bin folder of mongodb (C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.6\bin)
   -Run following command
     mongod.exe --dbpath "E:\Database"  (This path is your created folder path -step 2)
4. Start Mongo DB
   - -Open another cmd and go to bin folder of mongodb (C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.6\bin)
   - Run following command 
     mongo.exe  npm

5. git clone 
6. npm install
7. Run application 
   -Open node js  cmd prompt and run following command
     node app.js

8. Add following extension to google crome
   https://chrome.google.com/webstore/category/extensions?hl=en